---

## Troubleshooting Steps:

1. Created ticket in ServiceNow
2. Verified user identity via security questions
3. Remote session initiated using TeamViewer
4. Checked account status in Active Directory
5. Confirmed account is locked
6. Reset password in Active Directory
7. Verified user sync in Microsoft Entra ID
8. Asked user to login

---

## Resolution:
User successfully logged in after password reset and account unlock.

